Bc5 $11 {The position is dead equal}) (11. Nc4 {looks more active than 11.Nb3,
but now the d4-pawn is actually hanging.} exd4 12. a3 Bc5 13. b4 Bb6 14. Nxb6
axb6 15. Bb5 Nc6 16. Bxc6 bxc6 17. Qxd4 Qxd4 18. Nxd4 Bd7 (18... c5 $5) 19.
Rfd1 Rfd8 20. Nc2 Be6 {This endgame looks slightly better for Black, as the
