prepared for this typical advance} Ne4 $1 10. Bd3 {0-1 (47) Youssoupov,M (2233)
-Riff,J (2476) Chartres 2017} Nxd2 $5 11. Qxd2 Nf6 $15 {Black won the battle
for the e4 square and has the better game.} 12. Qc2 $6 c4 $17) 9... Ne4 $5 {
