Nxe4 16. Qxe4 Nf6 17. Qe5 {Now it's White who is looking for exchanges and
equality.} Qxe5+ 18. Nxe5 Bb7 $11) 11... Nxe4 12. Bxe4 Bxg3 $1 13. hxg3 Nf6 14.
